{"tid":1680044,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"禁制令新戰線，全部同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T16:18:20.000Z","uid":29148,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"419aecb754049b76acb8f3ee160cff802d36cd06","tid":1680044,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"對家不斷申請禁制令<br />\n等於直接抹黑手足<br />\n有無做過都已經上哂報紙<br />\n人地不斷進步梗<br />\n我覺得我地需要反撃<br />\n<br />\n第一，究竟申請人需要咩資格<br />\n第二，費用係點樣計呢<br />\n第三，大慨需要幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n另外，請集思廣益下<br />\n有乜野方向可以比我地做申請？<br />\n由我做起<br />\n<br />\n我建議要申請禁制令<br />\n禁止政府有關部門將交通燈關上<br />\n<br />\n我記得上次另外有個post亦有啲建議<br />\n有無手足做下整合？"},{"pid":"7b850a66ef79722db03dc99bb582a32704ee1e13","tid":1680044,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c798fb7a653e8cf4b05cf3d28160a3def12b1790","tid":1680044,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c2ac2b8b2c58c711a2dc33d146811625ece4d15","tid":1680044,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾YouTube玩雙重標準？移除修例風波真相影片？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679979</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8c6fd53e36370ca6e3177e4292524d164b18945","tid":1680044,"uid":334282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"想知，推"},{"pid":"fa55ddaa3a4173fbecdb68fcbd7979a16317566b","tid":1680044,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f61de531bdcfae6e42df8171304e21a7ee7c9836","tid":1680044,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"646ddefe87f6de91e4358a02e0009fb8579f2826","tid":1680044,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:29:55.000Z",